glossentry.glossdef:
A team that supports incident agencies by processing payments
			for resources. Resources may include emergency equipment, casuals,
			local vendors for supplies, etc.

The transfer of heat by the movement of a gas or liquid;
			convection, conduction, and radiation are the principal means of
			energy transfer.

A body of foam placed along areas to be protected from fire;
			also used as an anchor for indirect attack in place of hand-made
			fire line.

The top layer of forest floor, composed of loose debris of
			dead sticks, branches, twigs, and recently fallen leaves or needles;
			little altered in structure by decomposition.
